-- Spain banks have over 10 years to return EU loans: PM
-- 
-- Wed Jul 11, 2012 7:46am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/11/us-spain-economy-loans-idUSBRE86A0IH20120711

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - Spanish Prime Minster Rajoy said on Wednesday that banks will have more than 10 years to return European Union loans. 
 (Reporting By Sonya Dowsett; Editing by Clare Kane)